[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     4[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Date:** 2026-05-26
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     5[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Recipe file:** `chapter12.04-lab-result-trend-analysis.md`
