[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    70[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Expert:** Security (data classification, downstream consumer posture)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    71[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Location:** Step 5 pseudocode `deliver_trends` and Expected Results sample payload: the surfaced-trend payload includes `patient_id`, `most_recent_value`, `recent_values` (an array of date and value pairs), `baseline_value`, `explanation_text`, and `severity_band`.
